{"type":"message","id":"66ed7b2e","parentId":"821eeaa2","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:05:42.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！QVeris工作了！看起来之前可能是某些请求卡住了。现在我找到了finnhub的company news工具。\n\n但我需要找的是\"热点新闻\"或者\"趋势新闻\"，不是特定公司的新闻。让我搜索一下finnhub的其他新闻 endpoint，比如market news或者general news：","thinkingSignature":"5f588ffe3cd4c42d86a4a46682387c3c4fc1dfd2c3b5f64b289f497a8a93c8c9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_enz8e7upercu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --connect-timeout 8 -m 20 -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/search \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"query\": \"finnhub market news trending hot\", \"limit\": 10}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":10487,"output":169,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24640,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772528738692}}
{"type":"message","id":"fecb5018","parentId":"66ed7b2e","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:05:46.506Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_enz8e7upercu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\":\"finnhub market news trending hot\",\"total\":10,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.2e72ea5d\",\"name\":\"Market News\",\"description\":\"Get latest market news.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"category\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"}},{\"name\":\"minId\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"category\":\"general\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\"},{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.51b2567e\",\"name\":\"Market News\",\"description\":\"Get latest market news.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"category\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"}},{\"name\":\"minId\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"category\":\"general\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":2.911,\"success_rate\":1.0}},{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1\",\"name\":\"Market News\",\"description\":\"Get latest market news.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"category\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"}},{\"name\":\"minId\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"category\":\"general\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":807.31,\"success_rate\":0.997}},{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub.market.news.list.v1\",\"name\":\"Market News\",\"description\":\"Get latest market news.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"category\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"News category. Available values: \\\\`general\\\\` \\\\`forex\\\\` \\\\`crypto\\\\` \\\\`merger\\\\`\"},\"enum\":[\"general\",\"forex\",\"crypto\",\"merger\"]}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"category\":\"general\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1.874,\"success_rate\":1.0}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function name.\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"},\"enum\":[\"blockchain\",\"earnings\",\"ipo\",\"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\"financial_markets\",\"economy_fiscal\",\"economy_monetary\",\"economy_macro\",\"energy_transportation\",\"finance\",\"life_sciences\",\"manufacturing\",\"real_estate\",\"retail_wholesale\",\"technology\"]},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Sorting method.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":660.49,\"success_rate\":0.973}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\"description\":\"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\