lpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":660.49,\"success_rate\":0.973}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\"description\":\"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":883.34,\"success_rate\":0.946}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Financial News\",\"description\":\"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"}},{\"name\":\"t\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"}},{\"name\":\"offset\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"}},{\"name\":\"fmt\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1.183,\"success_rate\":0.741}},{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.dff02940\",\"name\":\"Insider Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"From date: 2020-03-15.\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"To date: 2020-03-16.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"to\":\"2020-03-16\",\"from\":\"2020-03-15\",\"symbol\":\"AAPL\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":3.579,\"success_rate\":1.0}},{\"tool_id\":\"alternative_crypto_fear_greed_index.fear_greed_index.retrieve.v1.fb14b8ee\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Crypto Fear & Greed Index\",\"description\":\"Fetch the current or historical Crypto Fear & Greed Index values from Alternative.me.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Limit the number of returned results. Default is '1'. Use '0' for all available data. The field 'time_until_update' is only returned when limit=1.\"}},{\"name\":\"format\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Response format: 'json' (default) or 'csv'.\"},\"enum\":[\"json\",\"csv\"]},{\"name\":\"date_format\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Date format for timestamps: 'us' (MM/DD/YYYY), 'cn' or 'kr' (YYYY/MM/DD), 'world' (DD/MM/YYYY). Default is Unix timestamp unless format=csv, in which case default is 'world'.\"},\"enum\":[\"us\",\"cn\",\"kr\",\"world\"]}],\"provider_description\":\"Provides a sentiment index for the Bitcoin and crypto market ranging from 0 (Extreme Fear) to 100 (Extreme Greed).\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1187.9,\"success_rate\":0.999}},{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub.stock.recommendation.retrieve.v1.b67c9ec5\",\"name\":\"Recommendation Trends\",\"description\":\"Get latest analyst recommendation trends for a company.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"symbol\":\"AAPL\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":4.791,\"success_rate\":1.0}}],\"search_id\":\"833f93ac-d4d2-4f65-9d08-22de655cff83\",\"elapsed_time_ms\":488.48}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772528821154}}
{"type":"message","id":"590254c9","parentId":"79a13e68","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:07:08.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了一个有98.7%成功率的工具：`alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1`，它可以返回新闻和情绪数据。让我执行这个工具获取最新财经新闻，看看是否有\"热度\"或\"相关性\"指标：","thinkingSignature":"7c289abc516c8592db545f8e2b7556f336600945270d09c0bbe09e2a4ba38493"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hg7u97pdvvlq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --connect-timeout 8 -m 30 -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/tools/execute \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\", \"params\": {\"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\", \"limit\": 30, \"sort\": \"RELEVANCE\"}}'","timeout":40}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":18380,"output":188,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32552,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772528821158}}
