{"type":"message","id":"feb6d8f8","parentId":"dd4553fd","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:07:43.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我成功获取了新闻数据。但用户提到\"热度≥80\"，这个数据中没有直接的\"热度\"指标。\n\n让我检查EODHD的数据格式，看看是否有类似\"relevance\"或\"score\"的字段，或者我需要解析这些新闻看看是否有\"热度\"信息。\n\n看起来数据中只有：\n- date\n- title\n- content\n- link\n- symbols\n- tags\n- sentiment (polarity, neg, neu, pos)\n\n也许用户说的\"热度\"是指sentiment的某种计算？让我看看是否能找到更合适的API。\n\n让我再尝试使用不同的参数调用EODHD news API，看看是否能返回更多字段包括热度：","thinkingSignature":"604f18f99385740080a6e1a737c11c2d4f86e35ddbaf7f5ade44401bd38a451f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e0shqbq96ofw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --connect-timeout 8 -m 25 -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/search \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"query\": \"EODHD financial news relevance score\", \"limit\": 5}'","timeout":35}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":26680,"output":242,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40906,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772528853160}}
